### Update Job Details

This endpoint allows you to update the details of a specific job.

#### Request

- Method: PUT
- Endpoint: {{host}}/job/:id
- Headers:
    - Content-Type: application/json
- Body:
    - name (string, required): The name of the job.
    - frequency (string, required): The frequency of the job.
    - retryLimit (number, required): The limit for job retries.
    - timeout (number, required): The timeout duration for the job.
    - priority (number, required): The priority of the job.
    - status (boolean, required): The status of the job.

#### Response

The response is in JSON format and follows the schema below:

